          <p class="alignment-block-content alignment-block-content-left original-text" data-text-version="original" id="orig-paragraph-0025">Go thou my incense upward from this hearth, </p>
          <p class="alignment-block-content alignment-block-content-left transformed-text hidden" data-text-version="transformed" id="trans-paragraph-0025">Go thou my incense upward from this hearth,</p>
          <p class="alignment-block-content alignment-block-content-left original-text" data-text-version="original" id="orig-paragraph-0026">And ask the gods to pardon this clear flame. </p>
